title: Barber Foods Recalls Stuffed Chicken Products Due To Possible Salmonella Enteritidis Contamination
summary: EDITORS NOTE: This release is being reissued to expand the July 2, 2015 recall to include additional products. Details of this release were also updated to reflect a change in poundage, epidemiological information and distribution area. WASHINGTON, July 12, 2015 Barber Foods, a Portland, Maine...
